\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11689985 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2111273\charrsid6632589 Where were you born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6098658 EJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2111273\charrsid6632589 At Bryn Terrace, Gwaelod Y Garth.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11689985 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2111273\charrsid6632589 How many years did you live in the house where you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6098658 EJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2111273\charrsid6632589 Ten. Ten, yes, mm, mm.
