I don't really know. No help with the washing. My mum was very fortunate always to have a bit of help though when - she was expecting the babies or if she was sick, there always seemed to be enough money for that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11689985 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2111273\charrsid6632589 Who would come, what happened when she was expecting a baby?
