 think. Yes, she was. And - I can't really remember anything very much, the most I can remember about that was when she was quite a baby, matter of weeks, mum was anxious to move down here, the house had been built, and the doctor, we'd an old doctor, we 
called him Doctor Thomas and he was a character I can tell you, and - he wouldn't allow because of rheumatism, he wanted the house to be thoroughly aired before - but I can quite remember - Llewellyn and Arthur being born. Oh very well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11689985 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2111273\charrsid6632589 What was it like then, was it different from now?
