 was gran - gran Davis and - arranged for mum to have this doctor and his wife for the birth - for Lennie's birth.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11689985 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2111273\charrsid6632589 You just called them grannies?
