\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6098658 EJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2111273\charrsid6632589 Yes, just the same, yes.
