\insrsid8807840\charrsid6632589 -}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2111273\charrsid6632589 stone cakes but the bake}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8807840\charrsid6632589 -}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2111273\charrsid6632589 
stone cakes the whole size of the bake}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8807840\charrsid6632589 -}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2111273\charrsid6632589 stone, and }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8807840\charrsid6632589 D}{\rtlch\fcs1 
