\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6098658 EJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2111273\charrsid6632589 No. I think we had - you know, an exce}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid338984\charrsid6632589 l}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2111273\charrsid6632589 lent home, like I think ours would have been - t
op rate compared with - lots. I dare hardly say this difference social group like - you know my friend, my particular friend was Margaret Berry the other side of the chapel, a minister's - daughter, well I mean - you couldn't really say that we were in th
e
 same social thing my, and yet we were big friends and we - did everything together and that. And that was only perhaps fortunately, perhaps - if I'd been brought up in a different type of home - very likely I wouldn't have mixed with the same type of fri
ends. Because that's how you find it isn't it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11689985 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2111273\charrsid6632589 Did the teachers single out some children for different treatment from the others?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6098658 EJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2111273\charrsid6632589 I think the poor were - poorer ones had a - the least chance of everything. Yes. And I think years ago too that if 
someone was a least bit stupid they had no chances at all. Now today there is a chance, in that they try to bring the best out - in everyone, but I wouldn't say years ago. I mean if you didn't - if you couldn't read very easy, well that was it, you'd prob
ably leave school not reading. They wouldn't put that little bit of extra put into it to help people, and I think if - if you had it well they'd help you but if you didn't, well just too bad.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11689985 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2111273\charrsid6632589 And there were gangs in the school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6098658 EJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2111273\charrsid6632589 I would say, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11689985 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2111273\charrsid6632589 What would they be composed of?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6098658 EJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2111273\charrsid6632589 Well various - say the poor - very poor ones a}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid338984\charrsid6632589 nd the dirty ones, well the dir
}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2111273\charrsid6632589 tiest would be together, and then I suppose - the poor ones, some of them they had no decent trousers or shoes or anything, they'd proba
bly feel self-conscious about being with - better dressed, and see there was quite a bit of that. You don't see so much of that today do you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11689985 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2111273\charrsid6632589 It was like that then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6098658 EJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2111273\charrsid6632589 Oh definitely. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11689985 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2111273\charrsid6632589 You went on then to a commercial school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6098658 EJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2111273\charrsid6632589 School, yes. A college.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11689985 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2111273\charrsid6632589 Where was that then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6098658 EJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2111273\charrsid6632589 Pontypridd. It was commercial and gen - and - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11689985 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2111273\charrsid6632589 How did you get there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6098658 EJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2111273\charrsid6632589 Oh pay, my mother had to pay for me to - join, mam had to pay for me to go there. I think mam - got to feel a bit better an
d thought well - I - had give - you know, sort of give me a chance again at something. And - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11689985 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2111273\charrsid6632589 Did you go straight there from the village school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6098658 EJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2111273\charrsid6632589 From the village school. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11689985 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2111273\charrsid6632589 And how long were you there?
