\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11689985 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2111273\charrsid6632589 So you were there four years?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6098658 EJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2111273\charrsid6632589 Yes. Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11689985 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2111273\charrsid6632589 It was not all that different from if you'd gone to the other one?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6098658 EJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2111273\charrsid6632589 No, not really you see. Well I - I suppose mam improved in health - you see, it was mam's health was so bad just at that 
time, I don't know whether she'd been told - about Lennie you see, this - this meningitis and had affected his brain, and whether it was because that she had a type of nervous breakdown, and - people don't see things straight then do they. Mm. And then of
 course by the time I'd finished my schooling there and got on and was really prepared I was going in for a secretarial course and that - then mam's health gave way again, and so I had to stay home and help then, it was just that sort of circumstance.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11689985 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2111273\charrsid6632589 She relied on you a lot did she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6098658 EJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2111273\charrsid6632589 Yes. Mm.
