re quite a little crowd going from - not to that particular school, but there was - a little - a boy a little bit younger than me going to a private school close by, and then there was a friend of mine - a little bit older - be two years - a little older 
t
han I am working in offices there. We'd go with about three or four going up together, because the girls going to the intermediary school were going the train earlier. Yes, they had to start - yes, they had to start a little bit earlier. Half an hour earl
ier.
