ther. Yes. Yes. And that's what I can't understand you see, mam had to pay for me to go to the commercial college. I just can't quite understand that. Though whether I would have missed - I don't quite know how they worked it at that time, if you'd go in 
at a certain age to the - to the intermediate perhaps, and perhaps I'd passed that age would you say perhaps. Could have couldn't it.
