\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6098658 EJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2111273\charrsid6632589 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11689985 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2111273\charrsid6632589 She had a breakdown when you were due to leave school again?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6098658 EJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2111273\charrsid6632589 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11689985 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2111273\charrsid6632589 She probably wanted you at home really?
